These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, van, trike
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person driving the jet-ski##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | van  | jet-ski | trike        | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, poppy, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who growstulip is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Flower   | sunflower   | tulip | poppy | azalea |

