.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, chaman, dunhill
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, house, indie
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of classical##7
3. the fan of house is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of indie and the aristoff-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | dunhill | chaman | vegafina  |
| Music-Genre   | house | classical  | indie   | dubstep |

