.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, balloon-flower, lily
1. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Flower   | bellflower      | amaryllis   | balloon-flower | lily  |

