.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, mango, lime
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating mango##1
4. the german is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person eating pepper##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food         | mango | pepper   | lime | broccoli |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

