.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, trike, bus
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the person driving the bus##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport      | motorbike | jet-ski      | trike | bus     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

