1. the argentine is on the far left##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar          | alhambra    | davidoff   | tiparillo | bluemaster  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

