.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, july, april
1. the argentine is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the spanish is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Birthday           | july   | april    | november       | february  |

