2. the person watching satire movies is not the malaysian##6
3. the turkish is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the french##5
5. the person watching family movies is the thai##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the thai##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Nationality           | thai    | turkish   | french  | malaysian      |

