2. the person eating garlic is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person eating raspberry is not the person driving the bus##6
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person eating raspberry##7
7. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food       | garlic | cauliflower | asparagus | raspberry |
| Transport   | bike   | trike      | bus        | subway  |

