3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
6. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
