The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the aristoff-smoker##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | baccarat | cain     | siglo |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 